'''Tobho Mott''' is a recurring character in the [[Season 1|first]] and [[Season 2|second]] seasons. He is played by guest star [[Andrew Wilde]] and debuts in &quot;[[Cripples, Bastards and Broken Things]].&quot; Tobho Mott is a master armorer and blacksmith in [[King's Landing]]. His apprentice [[Gendry]] is a [[bastardy|bastard]] son of Robert Baratheon. Tobho is tortured by the City Watch to reveal that Gendry fled the city in the wake of Robert's death.

